# Region Layout

| Component | Region | Why |
|-----------|--------|-----|
| ECR Repository | us-east-1 | Created by `terraform/cicd/`, shared across envs |
| Dev VPC, EC2, RDS | us-east-1 | Same region as ECR (simplifies networking) |
| SSM Parameters | us-east-1 | Co-located with compute |
| Terraform State (S3) | us-east-1 | Single state bucket for all environments |

> **Note:** Originally planned for ap-south-1 but moved to us-east-1 due to new AWS account EC2 region restrictions.

**Deploy script reads region config from `/opt/hestia/env.conf`:**
```bash
ECR_REGION=us-east-1    # Docker image pulls
SSM_REGION=us-east-1    # Parameter Store reads
```

