# VPC Architecture (Dev)

* **VPC:** 10.0.0.0/16 (`hestia-dev-vpc`)
* **Public Subnets:** 10.0.1.0/24, 10.0.2.0/24 (EC2 here, `map_public_ip_on_launch = true`)
* **Private Subnets:** 10.0.10.0/24, 10.0.11.0/24 (RDS here, no internet route)
* **Internet Gateway:** Single IGW for public subnets
* **Route Tables:** Public routes to IGW; private has no internet route (RDS doesn't need outbound)

