# CI/CD Pipeline

**Workflow:** `.github/workflows/ci-cd.yml` (manual dispatch with `deploy` input)

```
Job 1: Build & Test
  → Compile, unit tests, integration tests, Spotless check

Job 2: Docker Build & Push (ARM64)  [only when deploy=true]
  → OIDC auth → ECR login → buildx ARM64 → push to ECR (us-east-1)

Job 3: Blue-Green Deploy to Dev     [only when deploy=true]
  → Launch new EC2 → deploy.sh via SSM → health check → EIP swap → terminate old
```

**Deploy scripts:**
- `scripts/deploy/blue-green-deploy.sh` — Orchestration (runs in GitHub Actions runner)
- `scripts/deploy/deploy.sh` — App deployment (runs ON the EC2 instance via SSM)

